Comment: 10,0:06:42.78,0:06:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do this.
Comment: 10,0:06:44.25,0:06:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Comment: 10,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.
Comment: 10,0:06:47.45,0:06:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, and goodbye!
Comment: 10,0:06:49.08,0:06:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, now!
Comment: 10,0:06:56.59,0:06:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hannah and Barbara, yes?
Comment: 10,0:06:58.22,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to be back by six.
Comment: 10,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hitching a ride will get us right to the city. {there's an underlying feeling in this line of 'sensei can say what she wants about us not going, because this will take us there anyway'}
Comment: 10,0:07:09.88,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a genius!
Comment: 10,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 10,0:07:13.50,0:07:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot about Professor Ursula's lesson!
Comment: 10,0:07:15.94,0:07:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko, you can't make an omelette\Nwithout breaking a few eggs.
Comment: 10,0:07:19.77,0:07:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Sacrifices are a necessary evil.
Comment: 10,0:07:22.76,0:07:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You heard her.
Comment: 10,0:07:23.90,0:07:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it'll work out somehow.
Comment: 10,0:07:27.66,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay girls, we'll be spending some time together for a fun lesson today.
Comment: 10,0:07:35.89,0:07:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:07:41.75,0:07:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko! Akko!
Comment: 10,0:07:43.55,0:07:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost past the city.
Comment: 10,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! Oh, Lotte, you're in cosplay!
Comment: 10,0:07:47.74,0:07:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Comment: 10,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks great!
Comment: 10,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Comment: 10,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the city!
Comment: 10,0:07:59.40,0:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we're back on foot.
Comment: 10,0:08:00.95,0:08:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The magic dies off quickly once we leave school grounds.
Comment: 10,0:08:04.53,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing!
Comment: 10,0:08:09.80,0:08:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All the city streets are filled with {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}!
Comment: 10,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a dream!
Comment: 10,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Comment: 10,0:08:16.67,0:08:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there! It's the pirate waiter from volume 158! {lit 'waiter on the pirate ship', but he's clearly a pirate}
Comment: 10,0:08:20.65,0:08:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And over {\fax-0.2}there{\i0} is the bagpiper who dies in battle in volume 220!
Comment: 10,0:08:24.72,0:08:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the old loan shark who only shows up for one line in volume 37!{'one moment'}
Comment: 10,0:08:31.53,0:08:37.17,Default,,15,15,0,,Isn't that one of the 20 existing toothbrushes that came bundled with the magazine version as a bonus 100 years ago?{just way too wide}
Comment: 10,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll buy it for any amount you wish! \NGo on, name your price!
Comment: 10,0:08:39.69,0:08:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Comment: 10,0:08:40.76,0:08:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, excuse me!
Comment: 10,0:08:41.92,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte?
Comment: 10,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... amazing!
Comment: 10,0:08:45.81,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Great Ben, the clock tower\NBelle lived in at the very beginning of her journey?
Comment: 10,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I can trust anyone with a costume like yours with my life!
Comment: 10,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the first person to recognize me. {this is seriously like a real anime con, I'm feeling it}
Comment: 10,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I would, it's common knowledge!
Comment: 10,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's be friends!
Comment: 10,0:08:59.32,0:09:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Silly girl, we're already friends.
Comment: 10,0:09:02.35,0:09:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Comment: 10,0:09:05.03,0:09:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on around here? {the normalfag shows up}
Comment: 10,0:09:06.91,0:09:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is an event for {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}.
Comment: 10,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That worthless drivel?
Comment: 10,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How stupid must you be to dress up like that as an adult?
Comment: 10,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we stick around just to see\Nhow stupid they are for ourselves?
Comment: 10,0:09:17.78,0:09:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:09:19.77,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that it?
Comment: 10,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, it's over there!
Comment: 10,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it...
Comment: 10,0:09:29.26,0:09:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, girls!
Comment: 10,0:09:33.64,0:09:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is packed!
Comment: 10,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The crowd's bigger than I expected.
Comment: 10,0:09:36.96,0:09:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What made you become a fan of {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}, Lotte?
Comment: 10,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened back when I was a child.
Comment: 10,0:09:43.77,0:09:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My family runs a small magic item shop. {BD}
Comment: 10,0:09:47.94,0:09:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,One day, some of the local kids started teasing me because I was a witch.
Comment: 10,0:09:52.39,0:09:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That was when I first encountered\N{\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} at the library.
Comment: 10,0:09:57.31,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a reflection of myself in the vampire clan \Nthat was despised by humans and got hooked.
Comment: 10,0:10:03.51,0:10:10.49,Default,,13,13,0,,But I realized eventually that the werewolf Arthur was only making passes at Belle to get Edgar's attention.{## uh oh...}
Comment: 10,0:10:10.49,0:10:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't get that out of my mind.
Comment: 10,0:10:13.36,0:10:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I realized it, my own worries\Nseemed trivial in comparison.
Comment: 10,0:10:18.37,0:10:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm sure there must be many more people like me\Nwho felt like they were saved after reading this.
Comment: 10,0:10:23.26,0:10:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sorry, couldn't really catch that! Say it again?
Comment: 10,0:10:27.31,0:10:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}'s special event!
Comment: 10,0:10:31.19,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,To commemorate the release of {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}'s 365th volume,
Comment: 10,0:10:35.66,0:10:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the author Annabel will make her first-ever public appearance!
Comment: 10,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give it up for Annabel Crème!
Comment: 10,0:10:47.32,0:10:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! {\fax-0.2}She's{\i0} the writer?
Comment: 10,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she too young, even for a witch?
Comment: 10,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not just young, she's a kid.
Comment: 10,0:10:53.17,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she using magic to look like that?
Comment: 10,0:10:56.08,0:10:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute...
Comment: 10,0:10:57.67,0:11:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, Annabel! Can we have a word from you\Nfor your fans who have gathered here today?
Comment: 10,0:11:02.16,0:11:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 10,0:11:02.98,0:11:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A word for your fans!
Comment: 10,0:11:04.13,0:11:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Comment: 10,0:11:06.15,0:11:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Comment: 10,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who asked for a word.
Comment: 10,0:11:10.88,0:11:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So cold...{## meh}
Comment: 10,0:11:12.13,0:11:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What a cheeky brat.
Comment: 10,0:11:13.84,0:11:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So cute...
Comment: 10,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, let's move on to our next segment.
Comment: 10,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} quiz show!
Comment: 10,0:11:19.87,0:11:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Every question was personally made by Annabel to test your limits!
Comment: 10,0:11:23.39,0:11:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever manages to take first place will be awarded a fabulous prize from Annabel herself!
Comment: 10,0:11:29.19,0:11:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Question one!
Comment: 10,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This one's a softball.
Comment: 10,0:11:32.53,0:11:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the new address of the company that made the gloves given to Belle by her great-grandmother? {BD my most embarrassing mistake}
Comment: 10,0:11:38.82,0:11:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You know this, Barbara?
Comment: 10,0:11:40.55,0:11:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, no! I was just stretching my arm...
Comment: 10,0:11:43.25,0:11:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The fastest person was that red-hooded young lady!
Comment: 10,0:11:45.89,0:11:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,North Grampianshire, 43-5 White Street!
Comment: 10,0:11:49.33,0:11:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct!
Comment: 10,0:11:50.40,0:11:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, wow!
Comment: 10,0:11:51.26,0:11:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's keep on going!
Comment: 10,0:11:53.22,0:11:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Count Edward M. Winter!
Comment: 10,0:11:55.36,0:11:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,23678.9965!
Comment: 10,0:11:58.06,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Area code!
Comment: 10,0:11:58.97,0:12:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hexamine, potassium nitrate, and aqueous hydrogen peroxide. {literally homemade explosive}
Comment: 10,0:12:01.81,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,79 years and 2 months old.
Comment: 10,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally down to our last two contestants.\NWhich of them will claim victory?
Comment: 10,0:12:07.94,0:12:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you happen to be GreatBen810?
Comment: 10,0:12:13.40,0:12:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe she made it to the end.
Comment: 10,0:12:16.54,0:12:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, you can do it!
Comment: 10,0:12:17.84,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte?
Comment: 10,0:12:18.86,0:12:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's Lotte!
Comment: 10,0:12:20.83,0:12:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko and Sucy are here too.
Comment: 10,0:12:23.22,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, time for our final question.
Comment: 10,0:12:25.41,0:12:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel Crème's mother learned piano\Nfrom a certain teacher as a child.
Comment: 10,0:12:29.99,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Her husband's father's favorite bakery is named...
Comment: 10,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Somerset Bakery!
Comment: 10,0:12:35.78,0:12:41.18,Default,,15,15,0,,...and in that town there is a botanical garden. \NWhat is the name of the third flower in the planted area?
Comment: 10,0:12:43.05,0:12:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Was that really in there?
Comment: 10,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}What volume was it written in?
Comment: 10,0:12:48.73,0:12:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte...
Comment: 10,0:12:49.60,0:12:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like even Lotte's stumped by this one.
Comment: 10,0:12:52.40,0:12:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}I don't think it's a rose...
Comment: 10,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Not a narcissus either...
Comment: 10,0:13:02.04,0:13:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}Hydrangea...
Comment: 10,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydrangea!
Comment: 10,0:13:08.39,0:13:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct!
Comment: 10,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She got it!
Comment: 10,0:13:11.21,0:13:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We have our lucky winner!
Comment: 10,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please step forward.
Comment: 10,0:13:17.15,0:13:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She's all tensed up.
Comment: 10,0:13:18.31,0:13:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she'd be! I mean, she's right in front of her idol.
Comment: 10,0:13:21.92,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel's present is her favorite fountain pen!
Comment: 10,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You must really love {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}.
Comment: 10,0:13:28.66,0:13:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Comment: 10,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll gladly accept this.
Comment: 10,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the next Annabel.
Comment: 10,0:13:35.92,0:13:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:13:36.70,0:13:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} wasn't written by just one single author. I'm the twelfth Annabel.
Comment: 10,0:13:42.24,0:13:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've accepted it, you're the thirteenth.
Comment: 10,0:13:45.14,0:13:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't write, then your beloved {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} ends today.
Comment: 10,0:13:51.42,0:13:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's disappeared. What a staple of Annabel Crème.
Comment: 10,0:13:55.21,0:13:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's these unpredictable twists that make {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} so irresistible!
Comment: 10,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,A round of applause!
Comment: 10,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's all the time we have!
Comment: 10,0:14:04.05,0:14:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Didn't that seem kinda sudden?
Comment: 10,0:14:05.87,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty unnatural.
Comment: 10,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, she really got me there.
Comment: 10,0:14:12.90,0:14:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A magic item for teleportation...
Comment: 10,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea what to do after she vanished.
Comment: 10,0:14:19.81,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Comment: 10,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find her anywhere.
Comment: 10,0:14:23.84,0:14:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Think she's outside?
Comment: 10,0:14:26.91,0:14:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Comment: 10,0:14:27.86,0:14:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Comment: 10,0:14:28.82,0:14:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel disappearing wasn't part of the show. It looks like she used this.
Comment: 10,0:14:33.07,0:14:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Comment: 10,0:14:33.84,0:14:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A magic item.
Comment: 10,0:14:34.87,0:14:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Though it's more like a toy anyone could use.
Comment: 10,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Annabel isn't a witch!
Comment: 10,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 10,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I absolutely have to find her!
Comment: 10,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me look!
Comment: 10,0:14:45.39,0:14:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Comment: 10,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel? Annabel!
Comment: 10,0:14:50.51,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel?
Comment: 10,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel!
Comment: 10,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't find Annabel!
Comment: 10,0:14:55.44,0:14:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushroom. {fuckin laughed my ass off at this}{## i snickered loudly}
Comment: 10,0:14:55.97,0:14:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel!
Comment: 10,0:14:58.64,0:15:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Annabel, where are you?
Comment: 10,0:15:01.56,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushroom.
Comment: 10,0:15:06.16,0:15:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Find her?
Comment: 10,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she wasn't anywhere I looked. What now?
Comment: 10,0:15:09.95,0:15:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you need to find her so bad?
Comment: 10,0:15:11.61,0:15:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} wasn't written by a single author.
Comment: 10,0:15:15.43,0:15:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It was written by generations of people\Nwho inherited this fountain pen.
Comment: 10,0:15:19.57,0:15:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the fountain pen Annabel just gave to you?
Comment: 10,0:15:22.47,0:15:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 10,0:15:22.94,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that means you're gonna be\Nthe next writer of {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}?
Comment: 10,0:15:26.08,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't return it, then yeah.
Comment: 10,0:15:29.69,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Lotte!
Comment: 10,0:15:31.41,0:15:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 10,0:15:31.82,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It means Annabel passed the torch to you! {lit. told you to write the continuation}
Comment: 10,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess...
Comment: 10,0:15:36.80,0:15:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to write your favorite story yourself!
Comment: 10,0:15:40.27,0:15:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dream is about to come true!
Comment: 10,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never asked for that.
Comment: 10,0:15:45.10,0:15:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe that. You love {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} so much!
Comment: 10,0:15:48.58,0:15:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you that's not it!
Comment: 10,0:15:49.82,0:15:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 10,0:15:51.10,0:15:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you want to be like Chariot, {lit. 'be Chariot', not 'be like'}
Comment: 10,0:15:53.82,0:15:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never wanted to be like Annabel.
Comment: 10,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.83,Default,,15,15,0,,I don't want to do the same thing the person I look up to does.
Comment: 10,0:16:01.08,0:16:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She can do things that I can't.
Comment: 10,0:16:04.59,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I just enjoy cheering on people like that.
Comment: 10,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte...
Comment: 10,0:16:09.42,0:16:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I need to find Annabel as soon as possible.
Comment: 10,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is that fountain pen really old?
Comment: 10,0:16:14.51,0:16:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I heard that it's been used to write ever since the first chapter.
Comment: 10,0:16:19.17,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's that old, don't you think it should have a faerie?
Comment: 10,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Comment: 10,0:16:24.23,0:16:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte can talk to the faeries of old items.
Comment: 10,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's amazing!
Comment: 10,0:16:28.37,0:16:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too surprised.
Comment: 10,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Faeries dwell within old things.
Comment: 10,0:16:31.98,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned how to do it as a kid from my witch grandma.
Comment: 10,0:16:34.86,0:16:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure if it's possible here.
Comment: 10,0:16:39.01,0:16:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go somewhere else.
Comment: 10,0:16:59.85,0:17:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you. My name is Lotte Jansson.
Comment: 10,0:17:02.58,0:17:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know where Annabel is.
Comment: 10,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear anything.
Comment: 10,0:17:07.03,0:17:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Comment: 10,0:17:08.02,0:17:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Thank you.
Comment: 10,0:17:10.29,0:17:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd it say?
Comment: 10,0:17:11.49,0:17:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, it doesn't know.
Comment: 10,0:17:13.89,0:17:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Comment: 10,0:17:14.86,0:17:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But listen, it said that this fountain pen chooses each successive writer of {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}.
Comment: 10,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The current Annabel was chosen by this pen too.
Comment: 10,0:17:23.39,0:17:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems that she isn't confident in her own abilities.
Comment: 10,0:17:27.36,0:17:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She only held today's event to look for a successor herself.
Comment: 10,0:17:31.09,0:17:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And she ended up choosing you.
Comment: 10,0:17:33.25,0:17:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't accept that! {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}'s only been\Ngetting more interesting by the volume!
Comment: 10,0:17:38.43,0:17:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That means that the current Annabel's stories are amazing!
Comment: 10,0:17:41.41,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never accept a {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} written by anyone except her!
Comment: 10,0:17:45.17,0:17:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, let's go tell her that!
Comment: 10,0:17:47.98,0:17:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Comment: 10,0:17:48.52,0:17:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way Annabel could quit writing after hearing that from you!
Comment: 10,0:17:52.90,0:17:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Akko...
Comment: 10,0:17:54.09,0:17:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering how much you love Annabel, you should be able to figure out where she'd go.
Comment: 10,0:17:58.32,0:18:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Where Annabel would go?
Comment: 10,0:18:00.18,0:18:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah! Places she likes!
Comment: 10,0:18:02.80,0:18:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well, things she likes...
Comment: 10,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hydrangeas?
Comment: 10,0:18:08.76,0:18:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a bunch blooming over there.
Comment: 10,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She's close!
Comment: 10,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all the same.{## tattun is savage af}{i no rite}
Comment: 10,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I should head home now...
Comment: 10,0:18:24.01,0:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run!
Comment: 10,0:18:25.27,0:18:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Even if you beg, I won't take it back!
Comment: 10,0:18:28.03,0:18:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That fountain pen belongs to you now!
Comment: 10,0:18:30.77,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you should be the one to have it.\NIt chose you for your talent.
Comment: 10,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not talented at all!
Comment: 10,0:18:37.79,0:18:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's been saying that the latest\N{\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} books have been a train wreck.
Comment: 10,0:18:42.25,0:18:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I never expected Arthur to go to space...
Comment: 10,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,See?!
Comment: 10,0:18:46.43,0:18:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I was surprised, but he's been unconsciously wanting to go to space for the longest time.
Comment: 10,0:18:51.28,0:18:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like when his Oedipus complex\Nwas revealed in the past.
Comment: 10,0:18:54.76,0:18:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Experts have been predicting this for ages!
Comment: 10,0:18:57.00,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's something every fan knows!
Comment: 10,0:18:58.93,0:19:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We've always been waiting for this development!
Comment: 10,0:19:01.35,0:19:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just what a small part of the fanbase thinks.
Comment: 10,0:19:03.82,0:19:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I started writing,\NI've been flamed like crazy.
Comment: 10,0:19:07.07,0:19:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now {\fax-0.2}that's{\i0} only a small part of the fanbase.
Comment: 10,0:19:09.79,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The prison arc, the chapter when Belle caught a nuke with her bare hands,
Comment: 10,0:19:13.83,0:19:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the saga of them aiming for the a capella world championship were all really interesting!
Comment: 10,0:19:17.75,0:19:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like, how could you possibly not enjoy all that?!
Comment: 10,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I wrote those because\NI thought they were interesting.
Comment: 10,0:19:23.75,0:19:30.48,Default,,15,15,0,,But how am I supposed to stand back up when they say "stop writing" and "this sucks" and call each new volume worthless?
Comment: 10,0:19:30.48,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Comment: 10,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite book?
Comment: 10,0:19:33.87,0:19:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which book do you like the most?
Comment: 10,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Volume 363 when—
Comment: 10,0:19:39.22,0:19:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The one where Edgar lends Arthur his shoehorn?
Comment: 10,0:19:42.26,0:19:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I knew I wanted to write that one since I started!
Comment: 10,0:19:45.35,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Edgar hands over the shoehorn\Nwith his left hand, right?
Comment: 10,0:19:48.33,0:19:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,His clan believes that the left hand is a symbol of life.
Comment: 10,0:19:50.99,0:19:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And he handed him the shoehorn he received from his father with his left hand! That means—
Comment: 10,0:19:55.01,0:19:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Comment: 10,0:19:55.77,0:19:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I never realized!
Comment: 10,0:19:58.39,0:19:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Comment: 10,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea.
Comment: 10,0:20:00.63,0:20:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are a prodigy if you can\Nwrite that subconsciously.
Comment: 10,0:20:04.99,0:20:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I grew up reading {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}, so I really love it.
Comment: 10,0:20:09.28,0:20:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the same for me. I think there are kids like that all over the world.
Comment: 10,0:20:12.79,0:20:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're the only one who loves it more than anyone and also has the ability to add to it.
Comment: 10,0:20:18.88,0:20:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you stopped writing, then the real\N{\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} would be gone forever.
Comment: 10,0:20:24.09,0:20:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can write the {\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0} of our time.
Comment: 10,0:20:28.15,0:20:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can be Annabel.
Comment: 10,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I really do want to write!
Comment: 10,0:20:38.27,0:20:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Comment: 10,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.2}night fall{\i0}?
Comment: 10,0:21:03.55,0:21:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I saw her!
Comment: 10,0:21:05.05,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're crazy.
Comment: 10,0:21:06.36,0:21:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm serious! The cosplayer Lotte was talking to entered the leyline ahead of us!
Comment: 10,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be a Luna Nova student!
Comment: 10,0:21:19.23,0:21:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I presume you're prepared.{## little snitch academia}
Comment: 10,0:21:21.37,0:21:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Comment: 10,0:21:25.94,0:21:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a handshake from Annabel, but now\NI'm getting all covered in troll grime.
Comment: 10,0:21:30.53,0:21:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like you were even her fan before.
Comment: 10,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if I'm a secondary? {'niwaka' was thrown around a lot for kyoani fans a few years back}
Comment: 10,0:21:34.99,0:21:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, you can find all sorts of people in this world.
Comment: 10,0:21:38.29,0:21:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned a lot today.
Comment: 10,0:21:40.11,0:21:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking about Annabel? Didn't I tell you she was amazing?
Comment: 10,0:21:43.23,0:21:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you! You don't want to be like the person you admire, you want to support them.
Comment: 10,0:21:49.39,0:21:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never considered that before.
Comment: 10,0:21:51.60,0:21:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I still think you missed a big opportunity.
Comment: 10,0:21:54.22,0:21:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still saying that?
Comment: 10,0:21:55.43,0:21:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm glad it ended well, Lotte.
Comment: 10,0:21:57.39,0:21:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm really glad.
Comment: 10,0:21:59.74,0:22:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be spoiled on the story if I wrote it myself,\Nso there'd be nothing to look forward to.
Comment: 10,0:22:04.67,0:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Was that your actual reason?
Comment: 10,0:22:06.26,0:22:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how it goes. Let's hurry up\Nand finish cleaning already.
Comment: 10,0:22:12.49,0:22:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,GreatBen810, aren't you excited for the next release?
Comment: 10,0:22:20.67,0:22:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I start reading?
Comment: 10,0:22:22.88,0:22:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Comment: 10,0:22:24.43,0:22:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll save it until later.
Comment: 10,0:22:27.45,0:22:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
